Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:35.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Brought to you by \NLesKing.com.vn | Best place for Les and Trans Guys
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.00,0:00:42.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,DESERT HEARTS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.73,0:01:54.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.70,0:01:58.39,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Passengers of the super speed\Nservice to Sacramento and Oakland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.89,0:02:01.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,can now be on board.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:08.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Can I help you, miss?\N-Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.99,0:02:11.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'll bring this for you.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.99,0:02:20.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Professor Bell!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- You can call me Vivian.\N- Welcome to Reno.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.40,0:02:27.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I am down the street.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.10,0:02:30.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hi Francie.\N- Hello, Burnett.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.90,0:02:32.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- I have space in my car.\N- No, not such luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.30,0:02:39.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you are looking forward\Nto some desert living?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.01,0:02:41.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'am looking forward to get\Nthese shoes of.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible when\Nyour legs hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a kindest thing\NI've heard in three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.12,0:02:50.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- How long have you been married?\N- 12 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:54.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No,no. We handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.45,0:02:57.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Quint, that's a lucky one.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:00.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I could have used that last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.27,0:03:12.16,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,See you in six weeks, madam.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.17,0:03:14.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon as we are out of here you\Ncan tell me all about youself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.08,0:03:24.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I was the special dancer\Nin casino over there, 100 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:29.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have children??
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.90,0:03:32.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We were a couple of\Nprofessionals.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:39.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,My husband was a prominent lawyer,\Nhere in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.71,0:03:44.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- He died of a heart attack at 41.\N- Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:49.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.52,0:03:52.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not alone, I have my boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.43,0:03:57.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,My girlworks there\Nin the Golden Ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Has the unbridled\NGlen force!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.25,0:04:08.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I have always lived\Nin the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.15,0:04:11.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not know what to do\Nwith all this space.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.06,0:04:14.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I think of it as a God's backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.97,0:04:18.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just sit back and let\Nit clean out the impurities.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.88,0:04:22.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-And the heat?\N-Lot of ice tea and not deep thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:42.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-What are you doing at this hour?\N- I have things to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.50,0:04:47.40,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Professor Bell, Cay Rivers.\N-How do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:54.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Shall I call you the professor?\N-No, Vivian Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.32,0:04:58.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Put that damned car forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.23,0:05:04.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Jesus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll never guess who that was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.04,0:05:10.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Do you mind if I smoke?\N- Of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:13.85,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Never would have guessed\Nyou smoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.86,0:05:17.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,May I be honest, Frances?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.76,0:05:20.66,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That is an endangered art.\NForward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.67,0:05:26.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,My things are a little bit shaky\Nfor me at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.58,0:05:32.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Thank you for open up ...\N-I can not be a part of group right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.48,0:05:38.38,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.39,0:05:41.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:27.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Walter, we are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.21,0:06:35.10,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Walter, shake hands\Nwith professor Vivian.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:38.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Hello.\N-Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:41.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-You are younger than I thought.\N-I'll take that as a compliment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.93,0:06:44.83,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring bags, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.83,0:06:50.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You gona love it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.74,0:07:01.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.65,0:07:04.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice, isn't it?.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.56,0:07:08.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.46,0:07:10.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-He will take you to your room.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:27.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-The bathroom is over there.\N-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.28,0:07:30.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you teach?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.19,0:07:32.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Literature at the University\NColumbia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:35.99,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,116th Street, Broadway,\NNew York, New York.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:44.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you want me to hang around and\Ntell you history of the ranch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you guess, Walter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:51.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why I did not stay in a hotel?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.72,0:09:17.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt burned and start to yearn
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.63,0:09:19.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold you tight
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.54,0:09:26.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Guess what baby girl.\N- What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.44,0:09:29.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am engaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.35,0:09:31.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Hello\N-Hello, love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:33.16,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Isn't it beautiful?\N- Careful not to stay blind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:40.97,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pregnant.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe and I are settling down.\NDarrel and you should follow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:48.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-We would go on vacation together.\N-I feel nothing for Darrel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.79,0:09:51.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I never get tired\Nto defend your reputations.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.70,0:09:54.60,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I got used people\Ntalking behind my back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.61,0:09:58.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you did not accept\Nwho I am
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.52,0:10:02.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,that would really be tought.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.42,0:10:06.32,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.33,0:10:09.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And all the best people\Nknow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.24,0:10:48.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.04,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:57.95,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Would you like to play that, sir?\N- Sherman.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.96,0:11:00.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sherman, would you like to play?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.87,0:11:02.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer to play with you,\Nmy love.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.77,0:11:07.67,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Apologize to the lady, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:11.58,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Apologize, man.\N-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.39,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Thank you.\N-You are right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:19.30,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.31,0:11:42.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- A cup of tea?\N- Frances!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.22,0:11:46.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Do you have any burbon?\N-Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.13,0:11:50.02,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, I'll joing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.03,0:11:53.93,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Will not do any harm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.84,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.85,0:12:00.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I was reading a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.75,0:12:03.65,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like Cay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.56,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She locks herself in that college\Nand works until she drops.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.57,0:12:10.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-What does she work?\N-She is a sculptor.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.48,0:12:19.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't look at that stuff
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.38,0:12:24.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is sentimental junk.\NI have no taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.29,0:12:29.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Glen, Cay's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.20,0:12:33.10,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I had Walter with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:37.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not the mother of Cay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:39.91,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm her ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.92,0:12:41.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know what I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.83,0:12:46.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not anything really.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:49.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one pair of hands\Nand a familiar face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.64,0:12:54.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:58.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,God, look at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:01.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,As handsome as day is long.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:03.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And married.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.27,0:13:08.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I lived with him 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:15.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I didn't get my wedding\Nbouquet in my collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.09,0:13:17.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,But I got what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.99,0:13:20.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a love of my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.90,0:13:24.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That song is beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.81,0:13:28.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You had more than\Nmost people dare hope for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.71,0:13:35.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.62,0:13:37.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just babbling.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.53,0:13:44.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a silly woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.44,0:13:49.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you are, Frances.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.34,0:14:14.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You and me should make\Na raisins pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.16,0:14:24.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'm too depressed.\N-In this air?.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.07,0:14:26.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you well be fine when you\Nleave that creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:29.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Larry is not a creep
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Any man who leaves a woman\Nfor a model is a creep in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.79,0:14:35.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not know which is worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,A cheeter or a hobby man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,At least you can share\Na hobby, Lucille.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:44.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We would all like to\Nhave a different past.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:48.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:50.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.23,0:14:54.13,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I come down to stretch my legs.\N-It's was about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.14,0:14:57.04,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do in that room\Nfor last five days?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.05,0:15:00.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is, it is too deep\Nfor us to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.95,0:15:05.85,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, sit down.\NJoin the girl talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.76,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We talked about sex\Nvs. marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:12.67,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not an expert on these issues\Nso I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.67,0:15:15.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that your culture types\Ngo out like a bench sheet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:18.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Lucille!\N- Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.49,0:15:23.39,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,A bench sheet is a woman\Nweeping for the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.40,0:15:27.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps you wanted\Nto say "monkeys".
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.30,0:15:28.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.21,0:15:33.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll start with my pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.02,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucille, would you drop Cays' mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.03,0:15:40.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.93,0:15:42.83,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just going for a walk, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.84,0:15:45.74,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just slip it under her door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:53.65,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You do not have to knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.65,0:16:05.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Morning!\N- Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:27.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just passing by.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.47,0:16:32.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:39.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.65,0:16:43.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'd love to but you're busy.\N-Come in anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.56,0:16:51.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,To see if I can see it all\Nin one glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:54.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.47,0:17:09.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it if you are watching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.38,0:17:17.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello!\N- Hey....!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.28,0:17:19.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.19,0:17:22.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Where is Cay?\N-I am here. Go back to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.10,0:17:27.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I was not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.10,0:17:29.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine. Socialization\Nwas not what I had in mind, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.00,0:17:42.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You get all that traffic\Nwithout any equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.00,0:17:46.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.91,0:18:15.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Where are you going?\N-To an appointment with the lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No sense in taking two cars?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.73,0:18:20.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I do not want to intrude.\N-Will you bring her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.64,0:18:23.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, don't worry about that.\NGive space, Gwen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.55,0:18:27.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You have a car for today\Nand I save the trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.46,0:18:34.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cay, drive like a lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:37.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone used it as an ashtray.\NCome in front.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.27,0:18:46.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time without seeing you, Mrs. Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.18,0:18:50.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't bother me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.09,0:18:57.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-This is my friend, Gwen.\N-We met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, nice to see you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.90,0:19:20.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Are you serious?\N-Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:23.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That music is for a funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.71,0:19:27.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know that piece, Vivian?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.62,0:19:30.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it is a piece of Prokofiev.\NLovely, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.53,0:19:33.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I better get to the record\Nstore before they sell it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:37.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Gwen.\NWe all have sensitive side.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.34,0:19:40.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I do not remember that\Nyou said that last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.25,0:20:00.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Thank you.\N-Do you want me to wait?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:02.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure you have better things\Nto do than wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.07,0:20:03.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh look, I am sorry about Gwen.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.97,0:20:06.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You know why I am here for.\NI don't need to understand your friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.88,0:20:09.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the key here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:12.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I have more important things to\Nthink than how I'll go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.69,0:20:14.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks anyway!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.60,0:20:16.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.51,0:20:25.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,From what I see in this agreement,\NDr. Bell walks out with everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:27.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always supported myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.32,0:20:29.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,All I want are my books.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.23,0:20:33.13,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Is there a third party?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.14,0:20:36.04,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare women, walks out with\Nno strings.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.05,0:20:39.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What is your ground?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.95,0:20:43.85,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not that I have practiced\Nthis.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.86,0:20:48.76,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is not easy to talk\Nwith an attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.77,0:20:53.67,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Do you like ranch?\N-It's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:57.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,There are many crazy people there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.58,0:21:01.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Warner, I have 35 years.\NI want an honest life.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.49,0:21:03.39,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am leaving a decent marriage\Nto see if I can find one.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.40,0:21:05.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not having children helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.30,0:21:08.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Although our careers served very\Nmuch that purpose all these years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.21,0:21:10.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,To bond us togehter.\NWe were very big on form.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:17.02,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Right friends, a prince\Non the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.03,0:21:23.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I urge for something we can not\Nanalyze or rationalize.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to break free\Nfrom what I've been.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.84,0:21:32.74,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And your husband?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.75,0:21:36.65,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Martin wants to have me\Nno matter how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.65,0:21:38.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-He will not contest?\N-No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.56,0:21:41.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.47,0:21:46.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-We'll go with mental cruelty.\N-We've never treated each other that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.38,0:21:49.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a formal term.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.28,0:21:53.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is better for law.\NA headacke or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.19,0:21:57.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure he refused to\Nvisit in-laws, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.10,0:22:00.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll be alone\Nthe rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.00,0:22:04.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a very difficult decision and\Nit was not based on a headache or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.91,0:22:12.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for a martini.\NWould you like to take one with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.82,0:22:16.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.73,0:22:21.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the first thing I\Nadvise my clients
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.63,0:22:25.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,is not to leave the state\Nonce the residence is established.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.54,0:22:29.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Many leave to San Francisco\Nfor a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:32.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misunderstand me,\NMr. Warner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.36,0:22:34.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,But that does not happen\Nin this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.26,0:22:38.16,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I trust we can leave the\Nkeys with you any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.17,0:22:43.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.08,0:22:49.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, put your stuff in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.98,0:22:53.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock it up. The changing room\Nis over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.89,0:22:56.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Hello everybody. -This is Joyce.\N-Hello, Joyce!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.80,0:23:00.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave you with the girls.\NSee you on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.71,0:23:01.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:08.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cay, I'll like to see you in my office?\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Darrel, where shall I put the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.43,0:23:15.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Oh, God!\N-I'll tell you where.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:17.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Silver.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.24,0:23:20.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That was not very clever.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.15,0:23:28.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cay.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.66,0:23:38.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much I love you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.96,0:23:47.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I started to express myself\Nand ruined everything?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.80,0:23:51.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing to ruin, Darrel
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.65,0:23:55.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And I've been honest with you\Nabout why.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.56,0:23:57.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can look the other way\Nif I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.38,0:24:13.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.28,0:24:28.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Sorry.\N-Frances is awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.19,0:24:30.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I just thought about ...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.09,0:24:31.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,having a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.10,0:24:32.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me get it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:35.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't bother. I could\Nuse a practice.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.91,0:24:42.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you, please, go and\Nsit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.82,0:24:44.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If she hear us, I wont\Nget out in less than hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.73,0:24:49.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come back when it is less\Ncomplicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.63,0:24:54.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.54,0:24:58.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.45,0:25:01.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.36,0:25:05.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.26,0:25:10.16,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at my boots.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.17,0:25:23.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't\Nturn on the light.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.08,0:25:29.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What's matter?\NYou are having a rough night?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.98,0:25:33.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.89,0:25:37.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, I'm always awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.80,0:25:39.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time you can't sleep,\Ncome to my cottage.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.71,0:25:43.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Some company will help.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.61,0:25:45.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll make me cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.52,0:25:50.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No.\NI'm going to make you some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.43,0:25:56.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it you, Cay?\N- Yeah
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.34,0:26:03.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring me a coke, please?\NI have a glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.24,0:26:21.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Who is in the kitchen?\N-Vivian is making tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.15,0:26:24.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She is so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.06,0:26:26.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,This all place has risen\Ncategory since she came.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.96,0:26:33.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I spend all night\Nstruggling with migrene.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.87,0:26:37.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are wearing that one\Nout, Frances.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.78,0:26:42.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, everything is falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.69,0:26:45.58,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is middle of the night.\NIt will be together by morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.59,0:26:51.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.50,0:26:55.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What is falling apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.41,0:26:57.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,The ranch, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.32,0:27:01.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Business is bad. I don't think\Nit will hold much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.22,0:27:06.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember the good old days?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.98,0:27:09.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can not drink for the good old days.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.89,0:27:15.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If I do sell, I want you\Nto come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.80,0:27:19.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We do not picture us living\Nin two rooms togehter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.71,0:27:21.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, It will be bigger than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.61,0:27:25.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you come with me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.52,0:27:29.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You can leave the casino\Nand go to study art.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.43,0:27:34.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Botton yourself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.34,0:27:38.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor does not need\Nto see your business popping out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.24,0:27:41.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Where are your pants?\N-I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.15,0:27:44.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not stay so do not\Nsqueeze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.06,0:27:49.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You and Walter are all\NI have left from Glen!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.96,0:27:51.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.87,0:27:57.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, if I still have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.78,0:28:02.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday I will meet someone\Nwho counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.69,0:28:08.58,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Counts?\NBut look at who your friends are.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.59,0:28:11.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not ask your support. But\Nif you stand in my way ...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.50,0:28:24.40,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, go to sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.41,0:28:33.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I empty out my ice box.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.32,0:28:37.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, Frances.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.22,0:29:13.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.13,0:29:17.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.04,0:29:19.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,When was the last time you\Nride a horse?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.94,0:29:22.84,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.85,0:29:24.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, take off your reading\Nglasses and come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.76,0:29:47.66,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not know you were\Npainting, Frances?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.67,0:29:50.56,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,The last supper.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.57,0:29:56.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, looks like someone did not pack\Nriding cloths.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.48,0:29:58.38,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought my riding days are\Nbehind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.39,0:30:00.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. Try this to see the size.\N- Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.30,0:30:06.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Reserve me place in the mental\Nfor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.20,0:30:09.10,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good times are hard in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.11,0:30:16.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry about your friend\Nthe other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.02,0:30:18.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I temporary lost my sense\Nof humor.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.92,0:30:21.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is awful to forget\Nhow to laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.83,0:30:26.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always get-by by laughing.\NThat what you are going through\Ntakes real courage.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.74,0:30:28.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the first person to say so.\NEveryone else ...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.65,0:30:33.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, maybe, I am up\Nto the risk.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.55,0:30:37.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go. Maybe some of your\Ngambling spirit rob off on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.46,0:30:41.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that nobody accuses\Nyou of playing safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.37,0:30:43.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, but that is because they\Ndon't really know me.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.28,0:30:47.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,There are so many things\NI want to do but I am affraid to try.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.18,0:30:51.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-You're ambitious?\N- I do all right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.09,0:30:55.99,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's always another story\Nunder the surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.00,0:30:59.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- You know what I mean?\N- I am about to. My surface drowned.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.90,0:31:05.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Did you realise all your ambitions?\N-No. Only my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.00,0:31:09.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say when they ask\Nabout your marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.72,0:31:14.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I tell you that it sank in still waters.\N-Say no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.63,0:32:12.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot ass, Joe.\NCongratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.53,0:32:15.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What? With a ring costing $ 100.\NI need condolences.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.44,0:32:19.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-But her eyes are sparkling.\N-Not sparkling. It is panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.35,0:32:26.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiss me in a way to\Nlast me the entire shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.72,0:32:35.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Pervert.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.46,0:32:39.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Do you have a date, Cay?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.37,0:32:42.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up an extra steak, lover?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.28,0:32:44.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.18,0:32:52.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can not keep my hands off him.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.09,0:32:54.99,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And you invite me to your house\Nto watch the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.00,0:32:58.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find out\Nwhy are you so mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.90,0:33:07.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe is in the kitchen,\Nyou in the bathtub. I am happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.81,0:33:11.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, now start talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.72,0:33:16.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-You'll gonna laugh.\N-It must be serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.63,0:33:21.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I've found somebody\Nwho counts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.53,0:33:24.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,From the beginning\Nand do not miss the good parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.44,0:33:32.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, she is professor of English\Nand is 10 years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.00,0:33:37.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, rock'n'roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.26,0:33:39.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds a lot funnier than it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.16,0:33:41.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She is at the ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.07,0:33:45.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised not to mess around.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.98,0:33:49.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian Bell.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.88,0:33:52.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I just say her name\Nwhen I want to smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.79,0:33:55.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you sleep with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.70,0:33:57.60,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No. And probably will not.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.61,0:34:01.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-She does not want?\N-It's not that, Sil.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.51,0:34:11.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just remember that she will pick\Nup her decree and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.42,0:34:17.32,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe by then I will figure out\Nsomething in this screwed life of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.33,0:34:22.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I love your life, babe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.24,0:34:26.13,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be here without you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.14,0:34:33.04,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You look like two desserts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.45,0:34:35.95,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.96,0:34:41.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes I'd like to know what\Nis like to be a beautiful woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.86,0:34:44.76,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-You want the ring back, honey?\N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.77,0:34:46.67,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll be reincarnated.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.68,0:34:52.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to check steaks.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.50,0:34:54.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.49,0:35:01.39,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that if it will stay...\N... this good...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.40,0:35:03.30,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find a way to fuck it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.31,0:35:07.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Babe, don't we always\Nstick with good times?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.22,0:35:22.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Did Cay behave herself the other day?\N-She was absolutely charming.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.12,0:35:30.02,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I would not be too won over by her.\N-I do not understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.03,0:35:36.93,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing is ...\NShe has nothing in common with...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.00,0:35:40.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,a person of your caliber.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.01,0:35:51.74,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen this movie.\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.85,0:36:00.65,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We could stay here all day.\NI'll bring lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.66,0:36:01.56,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.57,0:36:03.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.47,0:36:08.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give me one?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.38,0:36:10.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No,no!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.29,0:36:15.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too big.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.20,0:36:20.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.10,0:36:28.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,He did nothing as a singer.\NSo I started to work in casino.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.01,0:36:31.91,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,In a hope of being discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.92,0:36:35.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Who named you "Silver"?\N-I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.00,0:36:38.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,But she still answers to Silvia\Nwhen she is wiery.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.73,0:36:42.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ignore that...\NCatherine Anne.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.64,0:36:44.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, oh here comes snake guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.55,0:36:48.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to track you down.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.45,0:36:51.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard you spent night...\Nafter Joyce.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.36,0:36:54.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,you got it backwards for\Na change.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.27,0:36:56.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,This is our friend, Vivian.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.17,0:36:59.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Whose friend?\N-My friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.08,0:37:03.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I am Darrel.\N-How do you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.00,0:37:05.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are probably doing better.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.90,0:37:08.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,So, when we are going to see\Nyou in that new outfit you just bought?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.80,0:37:13.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, I barely had the nerve to\Nbuy it...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.00,0:37:15.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,But Cay convinced me\Nto throw caution through the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.00,0:37:19.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what she is best at.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.53,0:37:22.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I am going to try\Nmy luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.43,0:37:35.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever was your intention,\Nyou accomplished quite the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.34,0:37:48.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I say, Cay steped way out of\Nher range with that woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.25,0:37:51.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want a tip?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.15,0:37:55.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Change your seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.06,0:38:15.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Thank you for really lovely day.\N-You are welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.97,0:38:19.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.88,0:38:33.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, my back is killing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.78,0:38:40.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was on 6 tranquilisers\Nbefore I got here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.69,0:38:44.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,The house, the kids,\NGale...all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.60,0:38:47.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? I am surprised. Your seam\Nso self assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.51,0:38:50.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank to Buck...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.41,0:38:53.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's amasing what a little "understanding"\Nwill do.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.32,0:38:56.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I do. Me and Cay are\Nbecoming friends and that does help.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.97,0:39:02.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not that it is any of mine concern,\Nbut you should think twice before
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.00,0:39:04.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,hanging out with her.\NYou are right, it's not your concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.04,0:39:07.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you know that she was kicked\Nout of College
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.95,0:39:09.85,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,for "unnatural acts" they say?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.00,0:39:12.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I rise up my\Neyebrows in gasp?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.76,0:39:17.66,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am definitely out to lunch\Nwhen it comes to queers. You?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.67,0:39:21.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think any of us would be\Nso limited, Lucille.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.58,0:39:26.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody said that it did not\Ntake all kinds, Vivian.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.49,0:39:29.38,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And your are certanly making\Na unique contribution.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.39,0:39:34.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Buck! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.30,0:40:05.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you winning?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.21,0:40:06.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.11,0:40:08.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.02,0:40:25.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't play,\Nyou can't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.93,0:40:30.83,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Buck!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.84,0:40:31.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.74,0:40:33.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.65,0:40:35.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough here. Put your bet.\NCome on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.56,0:40:44.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Down the way. Get your bet.\NYour time is my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.47,0:40:48.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here, darling.\NChange my luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.87,0:40:50.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No,no. Really,\NI don't know how to play this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.28,0:40:53.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I know how to play it.\NAnd I am down $200.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.19,0:40:57.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You just give them a nice shake,\Nand roll them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.09,0:40:59.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Put them in the air now.\NLet them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.00,0:41:02.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And get 7.\NRoll 7. Lets go.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.91,0:41:06.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That a winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.82,0:41:09.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That was beautiful, thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.72,0:41:11.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come again.\Nsame lucky lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.63,0:41:13.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.93,0:41:18.83,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner, winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.84,0:41:21.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah again!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.74,0:41:24.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner. Lucky day.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.45,0:41:27.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,This time blow.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.36,0:41:30.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this. And roll.\NRoll 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.27,0:41:39.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,2, and 2.\NNot good. Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.17,0:41:44.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.\NYou did fine. Take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.08,0:41:48.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.00,0:41:50.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you can.\NUse it to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.90,0:41:52.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Cash it in!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:54.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cash it in ot not.\NWhat's she gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.71,0:41:57.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Put bet down.\NHere we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.66,0:42:48.56,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.57,0:42:53.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Pat is having an engagement\Nparty tomorrow night.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.47,0:42:57.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I blame her.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.38,0:43:04.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we shall miss her with all\Nthis volgars going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.29,0:43:10.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I made your favorite, pancakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.20,0:43:13.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not going to like it.\NIn the middle of that circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.10,0:43:14.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not going.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.01,0:43:16.91,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Sensible.\N-Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.92,0:43:21.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I have lectures to prepare. I have only\Nweek and half left.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.82,0:43:23.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Have some fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.73,0:43:26.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Did Darrel put you off?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.64,0:43:28.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.00,0:43:31.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuss. Eat your breakfast and leave\Nthe woman alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.50,0:43:35.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't concern you,\NFrances! Honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.36,0:43:38.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are skating on thin ice, girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.27,0:43:43.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I wont you to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.17,0:43:51.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you resist such a\Npassionate request?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.08,0:44:13.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian, are you Ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.99,0:44:14.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Walk with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.90,0:44:19.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for not stepping\Nin and taking your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.80,0:44:26.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I surely wanted to.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.00,0:44:30.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Would you do something for me now?\N-Name it and it's yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.62,0:44:32.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are a wise observer.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.53,0:44:35.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does your mother dislike\NCay and I being friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.43,0:44:37.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants Cay all to herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.34,0:44:41.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Does she mind you and I\Nspend time together?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.25,0:44:44.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I dont' believe but\NI'll find put.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.15,0:44:46.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We are fated to be friends, Walter.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.06,0:44:49.96,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I felt that way since we met.\NCare for chicklick?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.00,0:44:52.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:55.00,0:44:59.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Based on what we just said,\Nwould you reconsider going tomorrow night?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.00,0:45:04.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I don't think I'll be comfortable\Ncelebrating with strangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.69,0:45:07.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am pretty sure Cay\Ncan get me invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:11.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you asking me to be your\Ndate, Walter?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.51,0:45:13.40,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not exactly my date.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.41,0:45:16.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know planty of girls.\NI just ask would you? That is all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.32,0:45:19.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you become\Nsuch a gentleman?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.23,0:45:21.13,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,The movies.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.13,0:45:24.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make an odd couple.\NI guarantee you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.04,0:45:27.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about\Nstupid oppinions.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.95,0:45:41.85,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Folks, may I have your attention,\Nplease?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.86,0:45:44.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.76,0:45:49.56,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like to welcome you\Nto this party of Joe Lorenzo.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.67,0:45:53.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Special applause for our\Nstar attraction. Miss Silver Dale.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.00,0:46:04.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop applauding\Nbecause I would like to sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.49,0:46:10.38,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote this song last week and\NI've been singing it everywere.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.39,0:46:17.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I wrote it ...  For everybody\Nthat I love in this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.30,0:46:20.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.21,0:46:27.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am holding you of the gorund\Nall the time I sing this song.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.11,0:46:33.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok boys, let's hit it.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.02,0:46:45.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to find someone\Nthat is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.93,0:46:49.83,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.84,0:46:54.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've tried a few, wouldn't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.74,0:46:57.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am so lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.65,0:47:02.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I hope these days end...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.56,0:47:06.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,and better days begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.47,0:47:08.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.37,0:47:12.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,for someone to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.28,0:47:18.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let the spark in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.19,0:47:21.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,to flame so bright...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.09,0:47:25.99,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,As I feel it burn I start to...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.00,0:47:30.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,to hold you tight..
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.91,0:47:35.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know I gave no sign...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.82,0:47:39.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,you must have read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.72,0:47:43.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.63,0:47:46.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,someone to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.54,0:47:50.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am looking for
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.45,0:47:53.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,someone
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.35,0:47:57.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,to love.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.00,0:48:03.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.17,0:48:53.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you dreaming about,\Nold lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.07,0:48:58.97,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Glen and me used to go\Ndancing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.00,0:49:01.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear that if I was to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.00,0:49:05.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,right now it's like\Nhe would be standing right behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.80,0:49:08.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why him and nobody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.10,0:49:13.60,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Beacause he reached in and
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.61,0:49:17.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,put a sting of lights right\Naround my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.52,0:49:26.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,These days are good and gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.43,0:49:30.32,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,But you are still the best\Ndancer in town.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.33,0:49:33.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You better believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:37.50,0:49:39.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.15,0:49:42.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Mrs. Parker, I am cutting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.05,0:49:44.95,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why? You go right ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.76,0:50:17.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why do you live at the ranch?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.87,0:50:20.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my hide out.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.00,0:50:23.67,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know all about hide outs.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.00,0:50:27.58,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you hiding from?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.59,0:50:30.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything I can't handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.50,0:50:33.40,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am relieved to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.41,0:50:39.30,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You know that I am not alowed\Nto go over State line?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.31,0:50:43.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I tell you what... What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.22,0:50:46.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If any rules get broken, I'll\Ntake the blame, ok?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:46.13,0:50:47.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.03,0:50:50.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I'll tell you what...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.94,0:50:54.84,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I...would prefer that\Nnone did.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.85,0:50:58.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Vivian.\N-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.76,0:51:00.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that you are loaded.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.66,0:51:05.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I could not imagine doing this\Nif I was not.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.57,0:51:08.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And what are you doing? Haa..
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.00,0:52:04.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-So, how long you've been with Darrel?\N-Not long.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.00,0:52:07.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What did hapen?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.29,0:52:10.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I alowed to myself to get attracted to\Nwhat is attraction to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.20,0:52:14.10,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-For him, that has been love.\N-And for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.11,0:52:18.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put it this way. I didn't\Nexactly get a ring.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.01,0:52:23.91,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-How do you get it?\N-With the woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.50,0:52:27.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are trying to shock me?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.83,0:52:30.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No. I was only telling you\Nthe truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.00,0:52:34.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I missled you in any way?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.64,0:52:36.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for the minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.55,0:52:40.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...you know I\Ncare a lot for you Cat, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.46,0:53:04.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Roll it all the way down.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.36,0:53:54.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.27,0:53:56.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.18,0:54:10.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn to kiss like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.09,0:54:15.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where they came from...\NIt belongs ... and I
Dialogue: 0,0:54:17.99,0:54:19.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk about it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:29.00,0:54:31.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.81,0:54:37.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I can't seea thing.\N-I'll take my chances.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.00,0:54:40.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Just drive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.89,0:55:10.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Are you ok?\N-I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.00,0:55:18.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...Looks like you two\Ngot caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.44,0:55:21.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We went for a ride to the\Nlake after the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.34,0:55:25.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Must have been quite a sight\Nto keep you up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.95,0:55:27.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody is checking in?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.80,0:55:29.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, somebody is checking out.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.07,0:55:33.97,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I made a reservation at\NThe Riverside.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.00,0:55:36.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Your bags are packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.00,0:55:39.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know that leaving the\Nparty would cause concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.00,0:55:44.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It also caused talk.\NHere is your refund check.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.50,0:55:50.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-That was uncalled for.\N-Oh, for God sake Francis!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.60,0:55:52.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you talk about God, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.51,0:55:56.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You made your point, Frances\NJust as well. I would leave anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:56.82,0:55:58.32,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.32,0:56:02.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:01.23,0:56:06.13,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let her come here with her books,\Nand her influence over my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.14,0:56:08.04,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Frances!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.92,0:56:12.94,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't claim angel wings,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.95,0:56:16.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,but I am normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.81,0:56:21.76,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And when I think... I was\Nproud to call you my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.00,0:56:24.67,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,May I tell you - betrayal is\Nmutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.00,0:56:31.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- I want to do that!\N- Walter, bring them here!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.00,0:56:36.48,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you find something\Nbetter to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:38.00,0:56:39.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not since you came on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.57,0:56:40.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.05,0:56:43.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.21,0:56:58.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.12,0:57:00.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.53,0:57:05.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be at Silver's.\NWill you call?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.93,0:57:10.83,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.00,0:57:36.74,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the only was to\Nsave my plants from
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.75,0:57:42.65,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,this damm disease is to buy a new one.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.66,0:57:44.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am moving out, Frances.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.56,0:57:48.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why?\N- To get your hands off of my life!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.47,0:57:54.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You sound like your father.\NUsing my place to hang your rat.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.38,0:57:57.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You want things without loving them!\NThat is greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.90,0:58:02.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't greed that took you in\Nwhen your mother left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.79,0:58:06.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It was not greed, it was\Nhis soul comfort for 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.10,0:58:09.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It is fancy word for what\Nyou really were!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.00,0:58:14.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It will be cold day in August\Nwhen I take in another educated tart!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.00,0:58:21.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She meant something to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.42,0:58:23.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And you knew it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.83,0:58:29.63,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She'd broke your heart,\Nthe one I ever...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.94,0:58:33.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no reason to stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.54,0:58:48.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your sweet lips
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.45,0:58:51.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Little closer to the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.36,0:58:58.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pretend that we are together...
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.26,0:59:01.16,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,All alone
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.17,0:59:05.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the man to turn
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.08,0:59:08.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,the jukebox way down low...
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.99,0:59:11.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.00,0:59:19.79,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-It's not complete.\N-How is that possible?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:26.00,0:59:28.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.00,0:59:33.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Over for tonight?\N-Yes, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.62,0:59:41.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.52,0:59:44.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...mine, I got to know.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.43,0:59:50.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Should I hand up
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.34,0:59:52.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,or you'll tell him he\Nhas to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.24,1:00:00.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't say the words I want\Nto hear while.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.15,1:00:03.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,you are with other man...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.06,1:00:09.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want me?\NAnswer yes or no...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.97,1:00:12.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Darling, I will understand...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.87,1:00:17.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Put your sweet lips
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.78,1:00:21.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,A little closer to the phone
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.69,1:00:26.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's pretend that we are togehter
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.60,1:00:30.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,all alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.50,1:00:34.40,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell the man to turn
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.41,1:00:39.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,the jukebox way down low...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:41.32,1:00:44.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can tell your friend\Nthere with you:
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.22,1:00:49.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,"You have to go"
Dialogue: 0,1:01:54.33,1:01:56.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Halo
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.04,1:02:00.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, Mr. Warner, it was\Nmisunderstanding.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:02.05,1:02:04.84,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.\NAccomodations are just fine here.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:06.85,1:02:09.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That will not be necessary, mr. Warner,\Nalthough I appreciate it.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.76,1:02:12.66,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need to get in touch with\Nme, I'll be her.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.67,1:02:16.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you. Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.58,1:02:45.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ok?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.48,1:02:50.38,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been better.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.39,1:02:53.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.30,1:02:58.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.20,1:03:02.10,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I am scared to death\Nof not seeing you again.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:04.11,1:03:06.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cay, you have to let it go.\NYou know that.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.02,1:03:10.92,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.93,1:03:14.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to open the door!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.83,1:03:17.73,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- And I want you to leave me alone.\N- I can't!
Dialogue: 0,1:03:20.74,1:03:21.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.65,1:03:35.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You look wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.00,1:03:41.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you kidding?
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.46,1:03:51.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, Cay.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.37,1:03:53.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.28,1:03:56.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You start.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.18,1:04:04.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.09,1:04:06.99,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And you kissed me.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:06.00,1:04:09.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And I kissed you, I know...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.91,1:04:12.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe what I am saying.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.00,1:04:14.71,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You see...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.72,1:04:19.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I enyoj order.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:23.63,1:04:25.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened between us...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:27.53,1:04:29.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,was innocent more than anything else.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.44,1:04:31.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And friendly. Don't forget that one.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.35,1:04:36.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I was really hoping that we can have\Nmature conversation about this.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.26,1:04:41.16,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,So far we talked about order and\Ndisorder and who kissed whom...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.16,1:04:44.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is it about anyway,\Nsince it was all innocent and friendly.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.07,1:04:46.97,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Than I'll get to damm point.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.98,1:04:48.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a respected scholar.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.89,1:04:51.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been married many years to\Nrespected scholar.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.79,1:04:56.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And for moment of indiscretion,\Nfleeding lap of judgement, I...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.70,1:04:58.60,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,stood in the rain and allowed\NFrances Parker...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.61,1:05:03.51,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,figure without any resemblance\Nto anyone in my entire life experience,
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.51,1:05:06.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,to humiliate us as we were pair\Nof deliquents.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.42,1:05:08.32,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have told her off.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.33,1:05:10.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a habit of rising\Nmy voice.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.24,1:05:13.14,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,or false issues.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.14,1:05:16.04,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,When I retire
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.05,1:05:18.95,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I will simply write short stories\Nfor my revenge
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.00,1:05:22.86,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,about this town, these\Npeople, these gamblers...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.00,1:05:31.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,My only clear memory is\Narriving.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.77,1:05:36.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is a blur...\NAbsolute blur.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.00,1:05:43.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.59,1:06:00.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think you\Nare doing?
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.49,1:06:01.39,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.00,1:06:14.30,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you tu put your cloths on\Nand leave.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:15.31,1:06:17.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-No you don't.\N-Yes I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.22,1:06:21.11,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No you don't.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.12,1:06:39.02,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.03,1:06:43.93,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.00,1:06:47.84,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You can start by putting\N"Do Not disturb" sign on the door.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.85,1:07:04.74,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,1:07:06.75,1:07:08.65,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That part went smoothly.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.56,1:07:14.56,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,So, take your hands out of your\Npockets and come here.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.57,1:07:37.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not...taking off my robe.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.00,1:07:42.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, everybody draws the line\Nsomewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.08,1:08:56.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't usually...
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.29,1:09:03.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,feel this way...\Nit's blocking me.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.20,1:09:14.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I felt\Nthis way ever before.
Dialogue: 0,1:11:19.50,1:11:20.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sorry.
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.31,1:12:47.91,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That goes the hot water.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.00,1:13:02.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Vivian...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.83,1:13:06.72,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to get out of here,
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.73,1:13:08.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,you know?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.00,1:13:09.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.55,1:13:12.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Take a walk.\N-I don't...
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.45,1:13:16.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Have a coke?\NWe go shopping?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:44.36,1:13:46.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You feel sorry?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.27,1:13:51.17,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-No, I feel exposed.\N-Because of me?
Dialogue: 0,1:13:53.00,1:13:54.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,And me.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:57.08,1:13:59.98,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how beautiful you\Nare right now?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.79,1:14:05.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any references for this.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:06.70,1:14:08.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I am not great at it either.\N-You had the experiences before.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:10.71,1:14:12.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Not this one.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.01,1:14:15.61,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,My life has always been so\Ncontolled.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.22,1:14:19.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-And it will be again.\N-Sure, of course.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.53,1:14:23.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,An affair, a divorce.\NNothing to break stripe on.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.83,1:14:27.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I love you.\N-And affair with 25 years old woman on my head.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:28.44,1:14:29.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.55,1:14:32.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure that students and the\Nfaculty will appreciate that.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:33.26,1:14:35.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,"These things happen".
Dialogue: 0,1:14:37.06,1:14:38.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:40.57,1:14:42.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Compliments of the boys.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.18,1:14:51.78,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Let's leave.\N-Oh, just relax.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.69,1:14:53.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Check, please!\N-We haven't had desert yet.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.00,1:14:56.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get desert from\Nroom service.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.60,1:15:02.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it, boys.\NThe night is still young.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:05.00,1:15:06.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Bye, honey.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.71,1:15:23.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, I am used to this.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:23.32,1:15:25.22,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am not.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.33,1:15:34.13,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, you are just visiting\Nthe way I live.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.00,1:15:38.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It suites you fine to hide in that\Nhotel room till your train leaves.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:39.04,1:15:41.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,By all means, let's hide.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.15,1:15:45.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so insisting that\Neveryone see the things you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:45.06,1:15:47.76,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah, made it really\Nlike that in your apartment.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.00,1:15:50.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No fear, no confusion.\NSo selfasured.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.00,1:15:53.66,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't act that way to change the world,\Nbut to goddamm world not change me!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:54.00,1:15:57.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Low your voice!\N-Why? is this a false issue?
Dialogue: 0,1:15:59.38,1:16:01.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there some way to make\Nthis easier?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.00,1:16:04.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Da
Dialogue: 0,1:16:06.09,1:16:08.29,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You take the car and I'll walk.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:08.30,1:16:10.20,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That is easiest as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.50,1:16:18.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have to turn\Naround this quickly?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:18.90,1:16:20.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Comes with the territory.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.00,1:16:29.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'll walk!\N-Its 18 km, Vivian.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.53,1:16:32.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!\NMaybe it will wake me up!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.67,1:17:33.74,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need me the way I need\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.55,1:17:36.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You know I do.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:13.35,1:18:15.55,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Sorry I am late.\NWalter couldn't find parking place.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.36,1:18:22.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Silver, you are gorgious.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:28.47,1:18:30.37,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Come on.\N-How long will it last?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.87,1:18:31.27,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,5 minutes
Dialogue: 0,1:18:42.28,1:18:45.18,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I am glad to see you, Walter.\N-I am glad to see you.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:47.19,1:18:49.09,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Thank you.\N-My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:49.50,1:18:52.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.\NIts Joe and Silvia.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:52.88,1:18:53.90,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Silver!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.91,1:18:57.81,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Joe and Silver,\Nwhere are you, nice people, from?
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.98,1:19:01.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Brooklyn.\N-Charlottesville, Texas.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:01.73,1:19:03.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,All pretty girl\Nare from there.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.23,1:19:07.53,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I will call upon gentleman upstairs\Nfor a very special blessing for you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:19.44,1:19:21.44,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-See me faint?\N-I cried all the way through.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.45,1:19:23.35,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It was really best.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.85,1:19:25.25,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cay is the best.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.17,1:19:33.07,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say I've never\Ngave you anything.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.58,1:19:38.97,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,- Have a good trip.\N-I see you in New York.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.98,1:19:40.88,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes you will.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.59,1:19:54.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Too bad that things didn't\Nwork out different.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.40,1:20:24.70,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Truth is that you don't\Nown me one damm thing!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.30,1:20:28.60,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothnig to hang on to\Nyou any more.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.61,1:20:31.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you, Frances.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:35.72,1:20:37.42,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never accept what you do.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.33,1:20:40.33,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.33,1:20:46.23,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I just don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.24,1:20:49.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Two women together!
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.15,1:20:52.05,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,She just reached in
Dialogue: 0,1:20:53.00,1:20:55.95,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,and laid a string of\Nlight in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.46,1:20:59.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't keep her waiting.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.77,1:21:02.77,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Frances, be happy for someone\Nin your life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:12.58,1:21:13.68,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, God!
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.18,1:21:18.58,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at us!\NStanding in the middle of the street.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:20.89,1:21:22.49,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Next thing you know they be\Ntalking about me.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.00,1:21:39.40,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it, then?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.21,1:21:42.31,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you longer than\Nanybody in my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.81,1:21:45.21,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,1:21:47.22,1:21:49.12,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That will never be it.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.93,1:22:24.03,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, congratulations, Vivian.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.04,1:22:28.93,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You return to New York\Nas a free woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.34,1:22:31.84,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless, of course, some\Nfellow here have stolen your heart.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:33.55,1:22:36.75,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-How about a drink, to celebrate?\N-I'd love to. But I have other plans.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.76,1:22:38.66,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Ok, I am sorry. I think I\Nunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.96,1:22:41.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You look different.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:42.20,1:22:44.47,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I see, you have found yourself\Na new pin pal.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.48,1:22:46.38,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I have much more than\Nthat, Mr. Warner.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.00,1:22:49.28,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.39,1:22:52.19,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck to you.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.70,1:23:05.10,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I talk you in to stay one\Nmore day?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.11,1:23:07.01,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Yes.\N-Do you want me to?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.00,1:23:09.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:11.12,1:23:13.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I'll come back.\N-When?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.83,1:23:14.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.04,1:23:16.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Christmas?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:16.84,1:23:19.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I don't know what you want.\N-It's you I want.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.55,1:23:35.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Cay?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.46,1:23:37.36,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,You are not coming?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:38.67,1:23:40.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll see you at the station.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:40.97,1:23:42.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we have dinner?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.58,1:23:44.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.09,1:23:46.59,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.82,1:23:49.91,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Because being with you is\Nstarting to hurt.
Dialogue: 0,1:23:55.62,1:23:56.82,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want...
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.00,1:24:02.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say goodbye alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:03.54,1:24:05.64,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been saying goodbye\Nfrom the begining.
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.30,1:24:11.54,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.95,1:25:33.45,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I put sugar...\N-I won't start.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.06,1:25:39.46,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-I got another postcard from Silver today.\N-How are they?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.47,1:25:42.26,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't all honeymoon cards\Nthe same?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.17,1:25:46.57,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,"Incredible divine. Just like\Na movie set. We'll never come back".
Dialogue: 0,1:25:47.20,1:25:49.08,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Come with me.\N-oh, sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.69,1:25:53.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really picture me with\Nyou?
Dialogue: 0,1:25:53.00,1:25:55.89,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want a sure thing,\Nstay in Reno.
Dialogue: 0,1:25:56.60,1:25:59.80,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,As for my friends\NI endured an hour with them...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:01.31,1:26:02.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Gwen.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.42,1:26:06.62,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a nice offer, Vivian.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.32,1:26:09.52,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,but there are still...a few\Nlosse ends...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.53,1:26:11.43,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-At least.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.44,1:26:13.34,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-Than, why did you make it?
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.45,1:26:15.24,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I care about you.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:15.45,1:26:18.15,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I think that you\Ndiserve to live somwhere with...
Dialogue: 0,1:26:18.96,1:26:23.06,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,or near someone who sees how\Nwonderful you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:24.17,1:26:26.97,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Know exactly who you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:28.08,1:26:29.87,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,"All on board!"
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.08,1:26:32.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,That is why I'll never\Nfinish this conversation.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:37.79,1:26:39.69,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,If it didn't please you, you\Nwouldn't have to stay.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.80,1:26:44.60,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we'll talk about that\None of these days.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:45.30,1:26:48.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me to the next station.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.61,1:26:50.41,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-What can we settle in 40 minutes?\N-I'll talk fast.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.50,1:26:56.50,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,Send me a postcard when you get there.
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.00,1:27:02.00,Size 30,,0000,0000,0000,,-What is it that you want?\N-Another 40 minutes with you.
